    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Ninjutsu </p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 8 (Spell Level 4)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 8</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 23 | <b>Successes:</b> 4</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 11 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 25</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> C, H</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>The target must have suffered damage from a piercing or slashing weapon before it can be affected by this technique, which makes the wound bleed, causing the subject to suffer 1 damage every round, which ignores all damage reductions. A creature can only be affected by a single use of this technique at a time.<br><br>Each time the subject receives healing from a spell, item, technique or the like, there is a cumulative 5% chance that the technique ends.</p>\n\n\n\n",
